{"tid":151434,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【深陷財困】傳樂視將上海物業50%股權售予融創","createTime":"2017-03-10T23:20:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-10T23:20:21.000Z","uid":17738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"eedd320c7d1997f90107eb708dadbb0f93b74d6c","tid":151434,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T23:20:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/11/071938_a4f54d55e360264e954a65463f8d5928.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F11%2F071938_a4f54d55e360264e954a65463f8d5928.jpg&h=0dc85f6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n深陷資金鏈斷裂危機的樂視，晚上於深交所發公告，由於樂視電子商務虧損情況不斷加劇，樂視網宣佈放棄前期樂視控股授予提案權、表決權；同時，樂視網放棄其尚未認繳的150萬元人民幣註冊資本對應的樂視電子商務15%股權權利，轉由樂榮控股出資認購。<br />\n<br />\n截至去年底，樂視電子商務負債總額高達14.3億元（人民幣．下同），公告指，自去年12月底起，樂視電子商務將不會納入公司報表範圍。<br />\n<br />\n另外，內地《21世紀經濟》今日報道，融創（1918）昨日協議受讓樂視控股持有的上海隆視投資50%股權，從而獲得上海虹橋商務區隆視廣場北樓物業的所有權；樂視出售項目股權的舉措被視為「自救」策略之一。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，消息人士未有透露交易作價，而根據同區虹橋中心於上月28日的一宗交易，以每平方米售價3.66萬元及財務費用計算，樂視與融創的交易價格或略高於此。<br />\n<br />\n掌握財經地產資訊，即Like「蘋果ATM」fb專頁啦！<br />\n<a href=\"http://fb.com/appledailyatm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2Fappledailyatm&d=BKn7HUA2FwSq4MnMa2nFTNibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=ff0f7cd0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://fb.com/appledailyatm</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56412023&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170310\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56412023%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170310&d=BKn7HUA2FwSq4MnMa2nFTNibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=e43ba8d0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56412023%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170310&h=20236f65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56412023&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170310</a>"}]}